data.title: How to Identify your iPad Model
data.text:
Click the iPad model name to get more information on Square’s Hardware compatibility.

You can locate your iPad model number by checking the back of your iPad.

iPad

iPad Air

iPad Pro

iPad mini

* Note: The following iPad models have a USB-C port which is not compatible with the Square Stand:

iPad Pro 11-inch (1st generation) or later

iPad Pro 12.9-inch (3rd generation) or later

iPad mini 8.3-inch (6th generation)

iPad Air (4th generation)

Please ensure your iPad has a Lightning connector type and check your iPad’s compatibility via our Device Compatibility page.
